{"tid":56060,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"發覺講普通話（國語）既人會顯得弱智","createTime":"2016-12-27T02:04:51.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-12T12:52:54.000Z","uid":58358,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"00ec28ec2b380a1a483eba5419a49802c651c61c","tid":56060,"uid":58358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T02:04:51.000Z","msg":"以下對話係用普通話進行<br />\n<br />\nA：我在香港吃了一個叫鹹水角(xian shui jiao)的東西，挻好吃的，下次你去也試試吧。<br />\n<br />\nB：不了，我不喜歡吃動物的腳 (jiao) ，太噁心了。<br />\n<br />\n「腳」同「角」同音同聲調 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7acf0156f3f955547714e2be975f3dd42725976a","tid":56060,"uid":22313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T02:10:52.000Z","msg":"做、坐、座、作，四個字同音，所以話普通話幾撚垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"080d11fe492752c2beade1d9b398db8b897e1786","tid":56060,"uid":5715,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T03:12:03.000Z","msg":"垃圾普通話想同粵語揮？差十條街"},{"pid":"0fbc78ad0cb803139af5b9b053df8d67a5b626ff","tid":56060,"uid":3197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T03:14:09.000Z","msg":"有咩名比你叫普通話 即是普通人講既話"},{"pid":"16f6be500fb6a7ccd17dc5bba81554fbd6575324","tid":56060,"uid":31501,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T03:19:02.000Z","msg":"可悲係政府迫人學<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/lomore_smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f811bd39d343b02c7bd7acc0f9fc5abcf805475","tid":56060,"uid":53577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T05:54:06.000Z","msg":"詞不達意，要靠聲調，作狀，扭曲，補充中文詞彙缺失。"},{"pid":"a175ec7535ef6c1b44cd173a61c7685bbe3fe026","tid":56060,"uid":66203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T07:03:53.000Z","msg":"國咩語呀 普通話就普通話啦"},{"pid":"652edfaf5e9292daa833e3a2082cec113f45660d","tid":56060,"uid":14758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T08:36:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>國咩語呀 普通話就普通話啦</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n虫話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e539cb6844f02f446dacefcea6bec66764e6d7ba","tid":56060,"uid":41245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T09:15:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>國咩語呀 普通話就普通話啦</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係囉<br />\n台灣人講 腳 同 角 唔同音㗎<br />\n中國人同台灣人會溝通唔到"},{"pid":"2fd4d64b0c49607a240e5110f640685cf71c8a55","tid":56060,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T12:17:03.000Z","msg":"因為同音/近音字多，要加多的字防混淆。<br />\n<br />\n例：一個億、『比較』乜，比較物，請勿-&gt;請不要等"},{"pid":"3eb8540749dc7e34e6094d1a7575663b04b1b1c0","tid":56060,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T12:19:12.000Z","msg":"垃圾蠻夷語言<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7ec0fb0d82748edcd663498c8512b06de9aec35","tid":56060,"uid":58358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-12T12:52:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}